            . The Prisoner at the Bar is a <rs id="t17451204-6-deflabel32" type="occupation">Sash-maker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17451204-6-defend115 t17451204-6-deflabel32"></join> by Trade, and I had many Times lost Lead, for he worked for me two or three Years, I began to be suspicious of him, and I told my Plummer, Mr. Bate, that I had lost great Quantities of Lead. Mr. Bate comes one Day and tells me of Lead that was bought of one 
